            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I've been torn between adding a param or just making some common vars to always return `/`. e.g. `HOME/VIM/VIMRUNTIME/PATH/CDPATH/TMPDIR/TMP/TEMP/MYVIMRC`. the latter would give users consistent `/` when using `$PATH / getenv('PATH') / vim.env.PATH`",
